        <h3 class="ui header">Description</h3>
            <p>
                I'm Hungry is a site that not only allows its users to discover and search for
                delicious restaurants wherever they are, but it also lets its users
                meet and eat with new people. Hungry and all your friends are busy?
                New in the city and want to explore? Through I'm Hungry, users can schedule
                times at their restaurant of choice and others can join in.
            </p>

        <div class="ui section divider"></div>
        <h3 class="ui header">Instructions</h3>
        <p>
            Site: <a href='https://ubfoodapp.herokuapp.com'>https://ubfoodapp.herokuapp.com</a><br>
            Github: <a href='https://github.com/TheNergaL/foodapp'>https://github.com/TheNergaL/foodapp</a><br><br>
            New users to the site must first register an account through the login page.<br>
            After registering and logging in, you will be greeted with the search page.<br>
            Enter a zip code and a keyword to search for restaurants.<br>
            A list of restaurants matching your criteria should appear.<br>
            Click on 'View Events'.<br>
            On the 'View Events' page, you can create new events or see and join events created by other users<br>
            by clicking the the 'Attend' button associated with each event.
        </p>
